node.text: This is a word guessing game from the creators of Exploding Kittens. It’s a game that forces you to speak in single syllables or you get hit with a stick. Link in story/profile.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by theoatmeal on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'THE PERILOUS PLIGHT ofthe MALE ANGLER FISH Originally published in 2010'.

node.text:
Praise the female angler.  Long may she reign. 

Originally published in 2010, this is an old comic of mine about my favorite fish.  Ze Frank eventually made a great video about anglers as well.  It’s on Youtube. 

Researchers have actually pulled anglers from the sea that they thought were covered in parasites, but turned out to actually be multiple sets of testicles.

node.text:
Today I published a long comic about the science and psychology of why it’s so hard to take compliments. Read the full thing on my website. Link in story/bio. 

The comic shown here was written by the wonderful James Miller of @asmallfiction

node.text:
Signup link to email newsletter in profile.

A big part of this decision comes from the recent news that Instagram wants to focus more heavily on video (presumably to try and become TikTok). This, in addition to Facebook trying to charge me $2,000 per comic to reach a fraction of my followers, I’m really trying to encourage people to follow me directly.
